trans-unit.source: Provides a reusable <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.UserControl"></xref> object for editing <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Udostępnia wielokrotnego użytku <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.UserControl"> </xref> obiekt do edycji <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection"> </xref> obiektów.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor> class provides a user interface for editing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elements of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> objects that are referenced by several different properties of controls at design time.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>Klasa udostępnia interfejs użytkownika do edycji <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>elementy <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection>obiektów, do których odwołuje się kilka różnych właściwości formantów w czasie projektowania.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The ParameterEditorUserControl class encapsulates most of the functionality of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>.
trans-unit.target: Klasa ParameterEditorUserControl hermetyzuje większość funkcjonalności <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor> consists of an enclosing form that holds the ParameterEditorUserControl, and **OK** and **Cancel** buttons.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>Składa się z otaczającym formularz, który przechowuje ParameterEditorUserControl, i **OK** i **anulować** przycisków.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> method adds an array of existing parameters to the ParameterEditorUserControl.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A>Metoda dodaje tablicy parametrów istniejącego ParameterEditorUserControl.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A> method removes all parameters from the ParameterEditorUserControl.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A>Metoda usuwa wszystkie parametry ParameterEditorUserControl.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.GetParameters%2A> method gets all parameters from the ParameterEditorUserControl.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.GetParameters%2A>Metoda pobiera wszystkie parametry z ParameterEditorUserControl.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.GetParameters%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A> method controls whether additions and deletions can be made to the parameters in the ParameterEditorUserControl.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A>Metoda określa, czy dodawania i usuwania mogą być tworzone w parametrach w ParameterEditorUserControl.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl"></xref> class using the specified <xref:System.IServiceProvider>.
trans-unit.target: Inicjuje nowe wystąpienie klasy <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl"> </xref> przy użyciu określonego <xref:System.IServiceProvider>.</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: The ParameterEditorUserControl constructor initializes the component controls of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object, initializes UI elements, connects events for the individual component editors, and adds the component editors to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A> collection for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktor ParameterEditorUserControl inicjuje kontroli składnika <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>obiekt, inicjuje elementy interfejsu użytkownika, łączy zdarzeń dla poszczególnych składników edytora, i dodaje edytory składnik do <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A>kolekcji dla <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.IServiceProvider> interface to the current design host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.IServiceProvider>Interfejsu na bieżącym hoście projektu, takie jak [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: Adds an array of existing parameters to the editor.
trans-unit.target: Dodaje tablicę istniejących parametrów do edytora.

trans-unit.source: The AddParameters method adds the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elements of `parameters` to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoda AddParameters — dodaje <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>elementy `parameters` do <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>kontroli w <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>obiektu.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>

trans-unit.source: If there is more than one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> element, the AddParameters selects the first one in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>.
trans-unit.target: Jeśli istnieje więcej niż jeden <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>element, AddParameters — wybiera pierwszą w <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>

trans-unit.source: Then the AddParameters refreshes the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control and raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: Następnie odświeża AddParameters — <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>kontroli i zgłasza <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged>zdarzeń.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter"></xref> array of existing parameters to add to the editor.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter"> </xref> tablicy istniejących parametrów, aby dodać do edytora.

trans-unit.source: Removes all parameters from the editor.
trans-unit.target: Usuwa wszystkie parametry w edytorze.

trans-unit.source: The ClearParameters method removes the parameters from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoda ClearParameters usuwa parametry z <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>kontroli w <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>obiektu.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>

trans-unit.source: Then the ClearParameters refreshes the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control and raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: Następnie odświeża ClearParameters <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>kontroli i zgłasza <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged>zdarzeń.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>

trans-unit.source: Gets all parameters from the editor.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera wszystkie parametry w edytorze.

trans-unit.source: The GetParameters method populates a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> array with all parameters from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>Tablica z wszystkimi parametrami <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>kontrolki <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> wypełnia GetParameters — metoda

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter"></xref> array of all parameters from the editor.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter"> </xref> tablicy wszystkich parametrów w edytorze.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ParametersChanged"></xref> event when the state of a parameter in the editor changes.
trans-unit.target: Zgłasza <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ParametersChanged"> </xref> zdarzenie po zmianie stanu parametru w edytorze.

trans-unit.source: The source of the event.
trans-unit.target: Źródło zdarzenia.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.EventArgs> object that contains the event data.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.EventArgs>Obiekt, który zawiera dane zdarzenia.</xref:System.EventArgs>

trans-unit.source: Occurs when any parameter or one of the parameter's properties is changed.
trans-unit.target: Występuje, gdy zostanie zmieniona żadnych parametrów lub jednej z właściwości parametru.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Do dodania.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether all the parameters in the editor are configured.
trans-unit.target: Zwraca wartość wskazującą, czy skonfigurowano wszystkich parametrów w edytorze.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if all parameters in the editor are fully configured; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Jeśli wszystkie parametry w edytorze są w pełni skonfigurowana; w przeciwnym razie <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Controls whether additions and deletions can be made to the values in the editor.
trans-unit.target: Określa, czy dodawania i usuwania mogą być tworzone na wartości w edytorze.

trans-unit.source: The SetAllowCollectionChanges method controls whether additions and deletions can be made to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> element in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoda SetAllowCollectionChanges Określa, czy dodawania i usuwania mogą być tworzone na <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection>element <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>obiektu.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection>

trans-unit.source: The SetAllowCollectionChanges enables or disables the Up, Down, Add, and Delete buttons but it does not affect the editing of individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elements.
trans-unit.target: SetAllowCollectionChanges Włącza lub wyłącza górę, dół, Dodaj i usuń przyciski, ale nie wpływa na edytowanie poszczególnych <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>elementy.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Boolean> that indicates whether additions and deletions can be made to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection"></xref> being edited.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Boolean>wskazująca, czy dodawania i usuwania mogą być tworzone na <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection"> </xref> edytowany.</xref:System.Boolean>
